options: {"symbol":{"description":"Ticker symbol used by the exchange"},"exchange":{"description":"Exchange acronym"},"google_symbol":{"description":"Symbol used in the Google finance network"},"e":{"description":"Exchange code used in the Google finance network"}}

name: interday
description: Historic data for a security on the Google network
options: {"symbol":{"description":"Ticker symbol used by the exchange"},"exchange":{"description":"Exchange acronym"},"google_symbol":{"description":"Symbol used in the Google finance network"},"e":{"description":"Exchange code used in the Google finance network"},"yahoo_symbol":{"description":"Symbol for security as used by The Yahoo! Network"},"yahooSuffix":{"description":"Symbol prefix used in The Yahoo! Network"},"interval":{"usage":"year|quarter|month|week|day","description":"The bar timeframe for the results"},"begin":{"example":"YYYY-MM-DD","description":"Sets the earliest date (or dateTime) to retrieve"},"end":{"example":"YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS","description":"Sets the latest dateTime to retrieve"},"marketOpensAt":{"description":"Time of day that the exchange options"},"marketClosesAt":{"description":"Time of day that the exchange closes"},"tz":{"description":"Timezone of the exchange formatted using the identifier in the tz database"}}
